## 3. Typography

### 3.1 Font Stack

| Role | Font | Fallback | Use |
|---|---|---|---|
| Display / headers | `Space Grotesk` | `system-ui, sans-serif` | H1–H3, section titles, wordmark |
| Body / labels | `Inter` | `system-ui, sans-serif` | Body text, UI labels, descriptions |
| Data / scores | `JetBrains Mono` | `monospace` | All numeric scores, hex values, timestamps, field names, IDs |

Load from Google Fonts:
```html
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
```

### 3.2 Type Scale

| Level | Font | Size | Weight | Color |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| H1 | Space Grotesk | 26px | 500 | `#FFFFFF` |
| H2 | Space Grotesk | 20px | 500 | `#FFFFFF` |
| H3 | Space Grotesk | 15px | 500 | `#FFFFFF` |
| Body | Inter | 13px | 400 | `#FFFFFF` |
| Label | JetBrains Mono | 10px | 400 | `#6B6B6B` — letter-spacing: 0.1em, uppercase |
| Score | JetBrains Mono | 12px | 500 | *(state color)* |
| Caption | JetBrains Mono | 9px | 400 | `#3A3A3A` |

**Label rule:** All section labels, field names, and category headers use JetBrains Mono, 9–10px, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.1em, color #6B6B6B or #3A3A3A. This is the signature text treatment — it makes data read as terminal output, not a generic dashboard.

