## 4. Component Patterns

### 4.1 State Badge
```css
.state-badge {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 3px 8px;
  border-radius: 3px;
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 5px;
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--state-color) 12%, transparent);
  color: var(--state-color);
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--state-color) 25%, transparent);
}
/* Exhaustion exception — always add explicit border */
.state-badge.exhaustion {
  border-color: rgba(232,232,240,0.25);
}
```

### 4.2 PRIME Badge
```css
.prime-badge {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 3px;
  background: rgba(212,168,83,0.18);
  color: #D4A853;
  border: 1px solid rgba(212,168,83,0.4);
}
/* Always prefix with ◆ character */
```

### 4.3 Score Bar
```css
.score-track {
  flex: 1;
  height: 4px;
  background: #1A1A1A;
  border-radius: 2px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.score-fill {
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 2px;
  background: var(--score-color);
  transition: width 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
}
.score-value {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--score-color);
  width: 24px;
  text-align: right;
}
```

### 4.4 Card / Panel
