## 6. Logo Usage

| File | Variant | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `logo_2.png` | Mark only (large) | App icons, loading screens |
| `logo3.png` | Mark only (small) | Compact placements, watermarks |
| `logo_1.png` | Mark + "Rhythm Engine™" wordmark | Primary brand lockup |

**Rules:**
- Always on `#0D0D0D` or `#000000` background — never on light
- Never add color — white mark only
- Never resize below 32px height
- ™ is part of the wordmark — always preserve it
- Minimum clear space: mark height × 0.5 on all sides

